description: This skill's purpose is to bring Sai Baba's hymns to Alexa. Shri Sai Baba is revered as one of the greatest saints ever seen in India.He transformed the lives of those who seek his blessings.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask Sigh Ram For Daily Bhajans
Alexa Open Sigh Ram and Play
name: Om Sai Ram
shortDescription: This skill invokes several short Sai Baba hymns. All these are publicly available hymns distributed by Shri Saibaba Sansthan Trust, Shirdi.
